
// Microsoft Power Platform for Power Apps Canvas
// To make a button to NEXT Record

// Inside a Power Apps Canva Screen1
// Command for OnVisible Event:
Set(iNumRecord,1)

// put a Form1
// Command for Form1 and Property DataSource:
tSales
// Command for Form1 and Property Item:
Index(tSales,iNumRecord)

// put a button Button1
// code for Button1 and Property Text:
GoNext
// code for Button1 and Property OnSelect:
Index(tSales,iNumRecord);
Set(iNumRecord, iNumRecord+1);

// Save Power Apps Canva Screen1
// PLays Power Apps Canva Screen1

